"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-[18px] font-medium leading-[26px] tracking-normal text-white/80","children":"As each program, initiative, and policy moves from 'Planned' to 'Live', this page moves with it. This is the direction we share to show what we're working on, and how it's going."}],"$L33","$L34","$L35","$L36"]}]]}]}]}]
