32:["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#4B5563]","children":"A public, live dashboard tracking the Government's progress against national priorities — so every Bahamian can see what has been committed to and where things stand. This is the accountability infrastructure the country has needed: not just a plan, but a visible, honest record of delivery."}]
33:["$","h3",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-white sm:text-2xl","children":"Three pillars. One purpose."}]
34:["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/80 sm:text-lg","children":"Modernizing government, preparing people for the future, and delivering on national priorities — all of it points in the same direction: more opportunity for more Bahamians. Wherever you live. Whatever you're building. However you got here."}]
35:["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/80 sm:text-lg","children":"If you want to be part of the work — not just watch it — we want to hear from you."}]
